          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈荣，杯内可有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见白银一锭，是老奴收下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赏与你的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢大爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈荣，大爷待你如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷待小人恩重如山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有桩心事要你去办，你可愿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要去得的，老奴焉敢不去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你三更时分，去到马房，将奎顺一刀刺死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，大爷！杀人之事，老奴不敢去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住口！胆大的狗才，叫你走东不敢到西。你若不去，活活打死你这老狗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我老糊涂了，此番去到马房，杀也在我，不杀也在我。嗯，自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣向陈文古。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，老奴愿去，只是无有利器。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈文古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有钢刀一把，杀了奎顺，方可见我；杀不了奎顺，死也不要见我！去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈文古下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈文古，好贼子啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈文古做事心忒狠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暗害好友丧良心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我岂肯为虎作伥做罪人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣下。陈碧桃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "屏风后面听言讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父亲为何把人伤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家、陈碧桃。在屏风后听爹爹呼唤陈荣，命他三更时分去到马房，将奎家二"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公一刀刺杀，我不免挡住宅门，候陈荣到来，问个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可叹我母去世早，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "撇下女儿受煎熬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要害奎顺为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不然一命赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等候陈荣问根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹行事太可恼"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我既知情救为妙"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将身站此宅门道"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老院公转来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "院公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是小姐。老奴叩头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站起来。夜静更深，你往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老奴奉了大爷之命，前后检点。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里是前后检点，分明奉了我爹爹之命，去到马房，将奎顺二相公一刀刺杀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是与不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘，老奴心事却被你猜着了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老哥偌大年纪，为何这样世事不懂？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老奴也是无可奈何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老哥，这有银子一锭，去到马房，杀也在你，不杀也在你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈碧桃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偌大年纪，你是懂事人哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈碧桃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，哎呀，小姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个贤德陈小姐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他比陈荣胜十分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后来必定是贵人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣下。奎顺上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泪似湘江水，滚滚不住流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生、奎顺。只为瑞霓罗帐，陈文古将我父亲害在监中，老母打入磨房，好不"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "气杀我也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一霎时急得我三魂不在，"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七魂悠悠又转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冤仇何日才得解开！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急急忙忙把马房找，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳听谯楼二鼓敲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狂风一阵灭灯苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "房内不见小儿曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈文古知道怎肯饶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他一觉睡着静悄悄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，看奎家二相公，竟此睡着了！也罢，待我老汉惊醒于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公有人行刺于你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄犬不住高声叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑夜间观不见路途道"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是何人把这风走了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东廊不见西廊去找"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来魂魄掉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跪在尘埃求命饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无仇杀我为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "结草衔环报恩高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄犬不住高声叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑夜间观不见路途道"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是何人把这风走了"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东廊不见西廊去找"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯饶命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有恩须当恩来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求开恩释放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公哭得如酒醉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁石人闻也泪抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈贼知道怎肯饶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他口口声声只叫饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒叫老汉无计较。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有恩须当恩来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求开恩释放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有恩须当恩来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求开恩释放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宁可人头高杆吊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉放你去远逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有恩须当恩来报"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求开恩释放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公，老汉不杀你，放你逃走了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本待将他释放了"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手执钢刀将他砍"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我还是杀的好放的好"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢老伯！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（奎顺下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走的好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（奎顺上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走不得！文古贼子，重重禁门，叫我往哪里逃走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，走不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公为何转来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，贼子重重禁门，我往哪里逃走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！这贼子重重禁门，叫他往哪里逃走！哦，有了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公，马房后倒塌一垛土墙，老汉送你那里逃走了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳老伯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公不必泪嚎啕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉言来听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遇着清官只管告"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯那厢有人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人，待老汉看来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是系马的桩儿，待老扶助你一把。"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高了上不去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我找个石块垫着，二相公帮我一把！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打了脚！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要高声！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好与你父母把仇消。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（奎顺上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走得好！一路之上，不知他可有盘费，待我叫他转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公转来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，我走的好好，叫我转来何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你一路之上可有盘费？"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，我不过是求乞而已！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公，你乃读书之人，焉能作求乞之事？老汉有白银一锭，带在身旁，也好"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做个盘费！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯大恩，请上受我一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒你说，这银子不是我的，是陈碧桃陈小姐的。你要拜，看绣楼上有红灯一"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盏，你与她多拜几拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（奎顺拜，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一下脱了身，走得好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（奎顺上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走不得，走不得！我走了不大要紧，陈文古向他要人，他把什么人交还？走不"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何又转来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，我走了不大要紧，陈文古向你要人，你把什么人交还与他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公，只要你脱身，休管老汉了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，我情愿一死，岂肯连累于你？将我杀了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个有志奇男子，他比陈荣胜十分。世间多少男儿汉，要想比他万不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二相公，那厢有人来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈荣自刎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "奎顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！受我一拜！"
        }
